    <summary>Handles the XML elements used to configure serialization by the &lt;xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer&gt;.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 This class is used to handle the [\&lt;dataContractSerializer\&gt;](../Topic/%3CdataContractSerializer%3E.md) group, which contains the [\&lt;dataContractSerializer\&gt;](../Topic/%3CdataContractSerializer%3E.md) element, specifically, to allow the addition of types to the collection of known types. For more information about data contract known types, see [Data Contract Known Types](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).  
  
 For an example of using the element to add to the known types collection, see [\&lt;declaredTypes\&gt;](../Topic/%3CdeclaredTypes%3E.md).  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
